<figureCitation id="13270BA9FFBF1B55F282F8E29A0FD22C" box="[1273,1348,1876,1898]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="5.[151,250,1804,1828]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,181,1780]" captionTargetId="figure-21@5.[151,1436,181,1780]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 2. Ampulicomorpha thauma Rasnitsyn &amp; Matveev, 1989, female from Iran (MOLC). A. Body, lateral view; B. Fore wing; C–E. Head; C. Ventro-frontal view; D. Lateral view; E. Dorsal view; F, I. Mesosoma; F. Dorsal view; I. Lateral view; G. Metapectal-propodeal complex, dorsal view; H, J. Metasoma; H. Dorsal view; J. Lateral view; K. Antennae." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6559817" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6559817/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="308">Fig. 2G</figureCitation>
